CSHandler - class com.topcoder.shared.netCommon.CSHandler.
The default CSReader and CSWriter implementation.
CSHandler() - Constructor for class com.topcoder.shared.netCommon.CSHandler
Constructs a new custom serialization handler.
CSReader - interface com.topcoder.shared.netCommon.CSReader.
This interface is used for reading bytes from a binary stream and reconstructing from them data in Java primitive types, selected Java Collections types and CustomSerializable instances.
CSWriter - interface com.topcoder.shared.netCommon.CSWriter.
This interface is used for converting from Java primitive types, selected Java Collections types and CustomSerializable instances to a series of bytes and writing these bytes to a binary stream.
